<super>mouse drag -> tile
<super>arrow -> tile
<super>right click -> resize

<C-shift>+ -> increase font
<C-shift>- -> descrease font

<C-shift>F11 -> full screen

<C-shift>n -> new window 
<C-shift>q -> close window 

<C-shift>t -> new tab 
<C-shift>q -> close tab 
<C-shift>right -> next tab 
<C-shift>left -> prev tab 
<C-shift>1..9 -> go to ith tab 

<C-shift>\ -> vertical split 
<C-shift-CP> -> horizontal split 
<C-shift>h -> left window 
<C-shift>l -> right window 
<C-shift>k -> up window 
<C-shift>j -> down window
<C-shift-alt>h -> resize narrower
<C-shift-alt>l -> resize wider
<C-shift-alt>k -> resize taller
<C-shift-alt>j -> resize shorter
<C-shift>w -> close window
